    empty or duplicated.

Daniele Forsi <daniele@forsi.it>	2012-07-12

    Don't check twice if name is NULL
    
    It is already checked after calling get_user_string().

Daniele Forsi <daniele@forsi.it>	2012-07-12

    Fix setting default width of main window
    
