Jorg Schuler <jcsjcs@users.sourceforge.net>	2009-04-18

* src/display.c           
  src/display_tracks.c           
  data/gtkpod.glade:           
    
  Clean up statusbar display in main window (remove resize           
  grip when statusbar is not at the rightmost corner).           
    
