    * display_coverart.c
    
    Null checks placed in free_album.
    g_hash_table_remove_all only used if running GLib version is
    newer than 2.12.0.
    Otherwise falls back on g_hash_table_foreach_remove.
    Thanks to Mario Rossi for squashing these bugs.
    
