    allow copying of tracks and playlists from within the
    context menu without using DND.
    
    git-svn-id: https://gtkpod.svn.sf.net/svnroot/gtkpod/gtkpod/trunk@1014 f01d2545-417e-4e96-918e-98f8d0dbbcb6

