    * removed mountpoint as parameter in itdb_write() as it was
    not used.
    
    git-svn-id: https://gtkpod.svn.sf.net/svnroot/gtkpod/gtkpod/trunk@648 f01d2545-417e-4e96-918e-98f8d0dbbcb6

