    Split up misc.c into more manageable files:
    
    wc -l src/misc*.c
    3195 src/misc.c
    ->
    wc -l src/misc*.c
    759 src/misc.c
    678 src/misc_confirm.c
    498 src/misc_conversion.c
    547 src/misc_input.c
    962 src/misc_playlist.c
    
