Jorg Schuler <jcsjcs@users.sourceforge.net>	2003-06-10

    date_parser are now actually interpreting the intervals
    specified. Valid:
    
    date < d < date
    = date
    > date
    ...
    
    Try it out (punsh in some string and press return)!
    
